> 
> Can anyone tell me if a method exists for saving device driver state during
> shutdown.  
>              Does anyone think this is a good idea?  
Yes, edit your startup and shutdown scripts to save and restor what you
like.
This is the beauty of Linux, your computer does what you want it to do
instead of what Microsoft wants it to do.
